---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Cookie Policy - Lewisham Your Party">
    <main class="min-h-screen bg-yp-cream text-yp-slate p-8 md:p-16 pt-0 md:pt-0">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            <a href="/" class="inline-block mb-8 text-yp-red font-bold uppercase tracking-wider hover:underline">
                &larr; Back to Home
            </a>
            <div class="bg-white p-8 md:p-12 shadow-xl border-t-8 border-yp-red mb-20">
                <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-heading uppercase tracking-tighter mb-6">Cookie Policy</h1>
            
            <div class="space-y-6 text-lg opacity-90">
                <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> 13 March 2026</p>

                <p>Unlike many modern websites, the Lewisham Your Party website is built on a "static" architecture. This means our site is designed to be incredibly fast, secure, and respectful of your privacy by default.</p>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold uppercase tracking-wider mt-8">1. What Are Cookies?</h2>
                <p>Cookies are small text files placed on your device when you visit a website.</p>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold uppercase tracking-wider mt-8">2. How We Use Cookies</h2>
                <p>Because of our grassroots tech ethos, <strong>we do not use any marketing, tracking, or analytics cookies.</strong> We do not track you across the internet, and we do not use social media pixels.</p>
                
                <p>We only utilize <strong>Strictly Necessary / Essential Cookies</strong>:</p>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
                    <li><strong>Cloudflare:</strong> Our website is hosted on Cloudflare's edge network. Cloudflare may place essential security cookies (such as <code>__cf_bm</code>) on your device to protect our site against malicious bots and DDoS attacks. These do not track your personal data and cannot be switched off.</li>
                </ul>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold uppercase tracking-wider mt-8">3. Managing Cookies</h2>
                <p>Because we only use strictly necessary security cookies, there is no cookie consent banner to dismiss on our site. However, you can manage or block all cookies at any time by adjusting your browser settings.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
</Layout>